Description:

This is a really working blog system. 
The code is referred from the link:
https://github.com/waylau/spring-boot-enterprise-application-development

1. All the backend code is new development based on Spring boot 2.0.3.RELEASE.
2. The frondend code has been referred from the above link with many bugs fix.
3. This blog system has the following dependencies:
  3.1. MySQL server to store blog basic contents
  3.2. MongoServer DB to store the images and user avatar files
  3.3. ElasticServer to support full text search
  
  



